Application Update

Hello {!Account.Name},

We are pleased to inform you that your application has progressed to the next stage of our recruitment process.

Your interview has been scheduled successfully.

Interview Name  {!Interview__c.Name}
Interview Date  {!Interview__c.Interview_Date__c}
Interview Type  {!Interview__c.Interview_Type__c}

Please be available at the scheduled time. We wish you the best for the next step.

Best regards,
Recruitment Team
